Application.Domain

Class Quiz

  • java.lang.Object
    • Application.Domain.Quiz

  • @Entity
public class Quiz
extends java.lang.Object
    Quiz is the class that maps the database Entity Quiz. A Quiz is a set of questions asked to a User to improve their understanding of the Scenario
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Corti Lorenzo, Tocchetti Andrea
